by.zyablov.airlinecompany.beans.company

Class AirlineCompany

  • java.lang.Object
    • by.zyablov.airlinecompany.beans.company.Company
      • by.zyablov.airlinecompany.beans.company.AirlineCompany

  • public class AirlineCompany
extends Company
    Class AirlineCompany represents a airline company, which includes id, companie's name, companie's email, companie's date of found and AircraftPark fields to storage Aircraft objects.

    AirlineCompany class inherits Company, this class allow to use AircraftPark object and works with it.

      • getListOfFoundAicraftsByFuelSpendingRange

        public java.util.List<Aircraft> getListOfFoundAicraftsByFuelSpendingRange(FuelSpendTonPerKm fromValueFuelSpending,
                                                                          FuelSpendTonPerKm toValueFuelSpending)
                                                                   throws AircraftEmptyParkException
        This method returns a list of Aircraft objects, which FuelSpendTonPerKm field from BasicTechAircraftData is enter the range between FuelSpendTonPerKm fromValueFuelSpending and FuelSpendTonPerKm toValueFuelSpending values.

        Also this method call's a getAircraftSet method from AircraftPark to get a set of Aircraft objects and uses compare method of AircraftComparatorByFuelSpending class.

        Parameters:
        fromValueFuelSpending - - a minimum FuelSpendTonPerKm value of the range
        toValueFuelSpendinga - - maximum FuelSpendTonPerKm value of the range
        Returns:
        listOfFoundAicrafts - a list of Aircraft objects, which FuelSpendTonPerKm field enter the range between FuelSpendTonPerKm fromValueFuelSpending and FuelSpendTonPerKm toValueFuelSpending values.
        Throws:
        AircraftEmptyParkException - indicates that AircraftPark object doesn't have Aircraft objects.

                                                                         KilometerPerHour toValueMidVelocity)

        This method returns a list of Aircraft objects, which KilometerPerHour field from BasicTechAircraftData is enter the range between KilometerPerHour fromValueMidVelocity and KilometerPerHour toValueMidVelocity values.

        Returns:

        Throws:

      • getAircraftFormAircraftParkById

        public Aircraft getAircraftFormAircraftParkById(int idAircraft)
        This method finds Aircraft object from a AircraftPark conteiner by unique aicraft's id field and returns this Aircraft object from AircraftPark conteiner. Also this method call's a getAircraftSet method from AircraftPark to get a set of Aircraft objects and use this set of Aircraft objects to find a Aircraft object with suitable ID field.
        Parameters:
        idAircraft - - value is a unique ID for Aircraft object.
        Returns:
        a found Aircraft object; null otherwise.
